{
  "stem": "27747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His wife and little boy were hiding, so they didn't find him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The photographer was taken out, and he was laughing and dancing, and they knew that he was crazy, so he was shot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the smith-- the smith, the blacksmith of the town, was a Jew also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He and his family were in the graves so [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they-- the Ukrainians wanted him to be freed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he said to the commandant, if you free my family, then I will go free also, and they didn't agree, so they were all shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This story was told by [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POLISH] was a man that his sisters were-- sister and brother were my schoolmates.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They perished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he had very good friends between the Ukrainians, and he survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war, he brought the bones, some of the bones, from the-- from that forest to Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Israel was established already in 1948.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when he came to Israel, he brought with him the bones, and they are buried now on the outskirts of Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came back to town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The town was really in terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The town was-- was-- the homes were emptied of possessions, opened windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we came to the pharmacy and found out that my cousin, the one that hid, that was the pharmacist also-- she's alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot of Jewish people were killed at that first action.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the action, it was-- nights were-- were just really sleepless.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sleepless.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the dreams were awful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many times, we just didn't know what to do, where to hide, what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
